                    <head>Visit Minister Ter Beek to Defense Minister FRG</head>
                    <msContents>
                        <summary>Report on the visit of Defence Minister Relus ter Beek to the Defence Minister of the FRG Gerhard Stoltenberg, and the possible implications of German reunification for the banking situation in Germany, NATO cooperation, and the CSCE discussions with the Soviets.</summary>
